Package codeContext.processors.export

Class ExportLocationAggregation

java.lang.Object
codeContext.processors.export.ExportLocationAggregation
public class ExportLocationAggregation extends Object
Manages aggregation of export locations with associated exported objects under one path for each file - export aggregation K-- export locations K-- export location K-- exports
